PPI::XS::Tokenizer
==================

This module is a C++ port for the PPI tokenizer
aimed for speeding up the whole package.
See the PPI::XS::Tokenizer.pm for usage details


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

PPI, ExtUtils::XSpp

